OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mainly
OL,6,Fdry, bright and warm evening, with the
OL,7,Fbest of the any late sunnier spells
OL,8,Facross southern Aberdeenshire.
OL,9,FRemaining dry for the rest of the
OL,10,Fnight with clear spells.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA dry and settled day, albeit
OL,13,Ffeeling cooler compared to Monday
OL,14,Faround coasts. Plenty of sunshine in
OL,15,Fthe morning before more in the cloud
OL,16,Fdevelops into the afternoon.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,19,Fdry and bright with a good deal of
OL,20,Fsunshine. Warm inland, but cooler
OL,21,Falong the east coast on Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
